In services choose VPC
Click on create VPC
Enter VPC name
Enter IPV4 CIDR Block
In IPV6 choose Amazon provided IPV6
Then click create VPC
Then choose subnets in the left menu
Create subnet, select VPC that you have created then click create a subnet
Go to the route table in the left menu
Create route table, enter the name and select VPC then create a routing table
Go to the internet gateway, enter your name and click create
Create a new instance with the newly created VPC as network and public VPC as its subnet.
Launch the instances
Create another instance with newly created VPC as network and private VPC as it is a subnet
Now launch the instances.
